# Hotel Performance Dashboard (Power BI)

## 📊 Project Overview
This project analyzes hotel performance using key metrics like Revenue, ADR, RevPAR, and Occupancy Rate.

## 🎯 Objective
To help stakeholders:
- Monitor hotel performance
- Make data-driven decisions
- Identify growth opportunities

## 📌 Key Metrics
- Revenue
- ADR (Average Daily Rate)
- RevPAR (Revenue Per Available Room)
- Occupancy %

## 🛠 Tools Used
- Power BI
- Excel

